OL,3,CIs Ruben Amorim the one to break the
OL,4,Cmould at Manchester United?
OL,6,FIf success comes with a winning smile
OL,7,Fand charisma, then Ruben Amorim might
OL,8,Fjust be Manchester United's man.
OL,10,FHe is the sixth permanent boss to sit
OL,11,Fin the Old Trafford hot seat since Sir
OL,12,FAlex Ferguson left and none of them
OL,13,Fhas been a resounding or long-lasting
OL,14,Fhit.
OL,16,FEach had an impressive CV but one by
OL,17,Fone they were sent away with little to
OL,18,Fcelebrate.
