OL,3,CIs Ruben Amorim the one to break the
OL,4,Cmould at Manchester United?
OL,6,FIs Amorim the one to break the mould?
OL,7,FCan he turn around a club that used to
OL,8,Fbe feared right across the league and
OL,9,Fis now languishing in mid-table?
OL,11,FHe believes so, but then you'd expect
OL,12,Fhim to say that.
OL,14,F"I'm a little bit of a dreamer and
OL,15,Fbelieve in myself," he said. "I also
OL,16,Fbelieve in the club. I think we have
OL,17,Fthe same idea, the same mindset so
OL,18,Fthat can help.
