OL,3,CIs Ruben Amorim the one to break the
OL,4,Cmould at Manchester United?
OL,6,F"I truly believe in the players also.
OL,7,FI know that you guys (the media) don't
OL,8,Fbelieve a lot in these players, but I,
OL,9,FI believe a lot. I think we, we have
OL,10,Froom to improve and I want to try new
OL,11,Fthings."
OL,13,FOn Friday at United's Carrington
OL,14,FTraining Ground, the conference room
OL,15,Fwhere Amorim was unveiled was as
OL,16,Fpacked as staffers here can remember.
