OL,3,CIs Ruben Amorim the one to break the
OL,4,Cmould at Manchester United?
OL,6,FAfter dithering over Erik ten Hag, who
OL,7,Fgot an unlikely contract extension in
OL,8,Fthe summer, Amorim is the Ineos
OL,9,Fchoice. The first big move from Sir
OL,10,FJim Ratcliffe and his executive team
OL,11,Fsince they took over running football
OL,12,Fmatters at United. They need this to
OL,13,Fwork.
OL,15,FAmorim has won the League twice with
OL,16,FSporting in Portugal, the first of
OL,17,Fthose ending a 19-year wait for the
OL,18,Fclub.
