OL,3,CIs Ruben Amorim the one to break the
OL,4,Cmould at Manchester United?
OL,6,FBut he's never managed a club outside
OL,7,Fhis home country before, and certainly
OL,8,Fnever experienced the scrutiny that is
OL,9,Fnow coming his way, but he does not
OL,10,Fbelieve this is the 'impossible job'.
OL,12,F"Call me naive, but I truly believe
OL,13,Fthat I'm the right guy in the right
OL,14,Fmoment," he said. "I could be wrong,
OL,15,Fbut the earth still will turn, the sun
OL,16,Fwill rise again."
OL,18,F"I truly believe that I'm the right
OL,19,Fguy for this job," Amorim added.
