OL,3,CIs Ruben Amorim the one to break the
OL,4,Cmould at Manchester United?
OL,6,FHowever, he did admit there will be no
OL,7,Fquick fix to turn United's fortunes
OL,8,Faround, saying: "I really don't know
OL,9,Fthe biggest challenge. I will find out
OL,10,Fduring this month.
OL,12,F"You had here different types of
OL,13,Fcoaches, so the guys that won
OL,14,Feverything like Van Gaal and Mourinho.
OL,15,FYou've had new ones like they knew the
OL,16,Fclub inside out like Solskjaer. Then
OL,17,Fyou have one of the best that there
OL,18,Fwill ever be in the outside, the five
OL,19,Fstrongest leagues - Ten Hag."
