OL,11,F"I don't know, I think we have to
OL,12,Fimprove as a club. We have to
OL,13,Facknowledge that we are in the time
OL,14,Fthat we need time and every coach that
OL,15,Fcomes here needs time," Amorim said.
OL,17,F"But to acknowledge that we also have
OL,18,Fto win games and that's it. We will
OL,19,Ftry to do it our way, in my way and
OL,20,Ftry to win it."
